{"tid":1560697,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"通識概念分享-性別定型","createTime":"2019-09-11T10:10:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T10:23:09.000Z","uid":257845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b2abcceb3af76313d65b1e99baca4829ae0bcef5","tid":1560697,"uid":257845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:10:10.000Z","msg":"相關單元：個人成長與人際關係<br />\n<br />\n何謂性別定型？<br />\n性別定型是指把一些對大部分男性和女性均有的特質作出定型，並從而規範看兩性的行為、性格和價值觀。<br />\n<br />\n傳統上認為男性應該剛強堅毅、較粗魯、有幹勁和魄力、不太愛美和打扮、較理性、以事業為重、家庭經濟支柱、保護者。<br />\n<br />\n傳統上認為女性應該斯文、温婉賢淑、喜歡打扮、感性、較被動、以家庭為重、<br />\n料理家務及照顧家人、被保護者。<br />\n<br />\n若青少年有性別認同障礙，或對成長發展帶來的負面影響，包括：<br />\n1. 當發現自己思想和行為跟他人對自己的期望存在矛盾和衝突時，就造成心理壓力。<br />\n2. 因自己的生理性別與心理上認同的性別不相同而感到疑惑，令到選擇個人身份角色時感到困難。<br />\n3. 行舉止跟社會對他的性別期望並不相符時，可能會受到各方的嘲笑、怪責和負面批評，自我形象受損，自尊感低落。<br />\n4. 朋友不接納及排擠，會使到性別認同障礙人士人際關係受損，缺乏他人的接納和認同，也缺乏歸屬感。<br />\n<br />\n過去相關試題：<br />\n參考以上資料，你在多大程度上認為在情人節時送花反映了香港社會上的性別定型？解釋你的答案。 (10分)<br />\n*2012通識教育練習卷題目資料可參考考評局網站：<a href=\"http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/DocLibrary/HKDSE/Practice_Paper/LS/HKDSE_LS_PP_20120116_chi.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkeaa.edu.hk%2FDocLibrary%2FHKDSE%2FPractice_Paper%2FLS%2FHKDSE_LS_PP_20120116_chi.pdf&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWW2%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=554fe5b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/DocLibrary/HKDSE/Practice_Paper/LS/HKDSE_LS_PP_20120116_chi.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位如有問題，可以隨時PM我！<br />\n利申：2年通識5**/通識教師"},{"pid":"4e11cfb2b962bb7a004bf7188c3fad02e8f4f357","tid":1560697,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:10:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"e3e3fca285941d6d783b04c6184ce9df8cbf03fa","tid":1560697,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:13:12.000Z","msg":"【保民聯】建制保皇 建設保民 香港值得更好的建設派<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1560300\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1560300</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2edu5dD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2edu5dD.png&h=f7e4a997&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e17af777d2074ec908da7e8a2b7e59c82fee6cf0","tid":1560697,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:16:36.000Z","msg":"唔好再簡單啲"},{"pid":"dd4d71b603ba9396ab1d35783680039fa4583d19","tid":1560697,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:23:09.000Z","msg":"請問資本主義同黃藍絲嘅政見有咩關係？"}]}